      "text": "Grid Trading Engine\n├── ETH/SOL/TAO Futures\n├── 4-level grid per pair\n├── Regime Detector (Hurst/ADX)\n├── Learning Engine (~84h cycle)\n├── 10-layer Risk Guards\n├── News Guard + Whale Alerts\n├── Funding Rate Bias\n└── Dashboard :4201\n\n📊 trading.db (SQLite WAL)\n🤖 Telegram @El_pesos_bot",
