      "height": 130,
      "text": "├── Watchdog        (every 30s)  → probe El Pesos health\n├── Signal Processor (every 60s)  → read → resolve → apply\n├── MiroFish Trigger (every 4h)   → swarm prediction\n├── Autoresearch     (every 12h)  → backtest optimization\n├── Goal Evaluator   (Sundays)    → self-evolving targets\n├── Conflict Resolver              → higher conf wins (-20%)\n├── Confidence Tracker             → 1.0x base → 1.5x max\n└── Dashboard :4203                → command center UI",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "strokeColor": "#d4d4d8"
