      "text": "Karpathy Loop:\n\n1. Load 30-day patterns\n2. Propose param change\n   (60% pattern-guided)\n3. Backtest 7-day window\n4. Score composite metric\n5. Keep if >2% better\n6. Auto-apply via signal\n7. Repeat (20 iters/cycle)",
